name: Saint Christopher
description:
2021 | 2120 x 3276 Pixels | 9 Pixels/inch | sRGB | Adobe Photoshop + Illustrator 

Saint Christopher is an interpretation of a devotional medal to bless travelers on their journey. By interacting on the blockchain we travel too. May this medal keep you safe.

Wikipedia says: Devotional medals with Saint Christopher‘s name and image are commonly worn as pendants, especially by travelers, to show devotion and as a request for his blessing.
